37:29.080 --> 37:30.782
$500,000 is a lot.

37:30.782 --> 37:32.283
What are you using
the money for?

37:32.283 --> 37:34.652
So the money that we're going to
get, you know,

37:34.652 --> 37:36.187
when we get this deal, right,

37:36.187 --> 37:38.123
