38:02.013 --> 38:03.448
That's what I need to know.

38:03.448 --> 38:05.283
Hiring artists to basically
build this pipeline.

38:05.283 --> 38:06.818
We need writers, too,
and everything else.

38:06.818 --> 38:08.987
These artists are like
$30,000, $40,000 each,

38:08.987 --> 38:10.321
every single year.

38:10.321 --> 38:11.356
All right, guys.

38:11.356 --> 38:12.524
I do understand
what you're doing

38:12.524 --> 38:13.825
