So I'm just going
to tell you the value

38:25.670 --> 38:29.107
I feel like I'm bringing to you
before I give you my offer.

38:29.107 --> 38:32.744
Okay? I own distribution
in the world of audio.

38:32.744 --> 38:35.480
I own distribution
in the world of television.

38:35.480 --> 38:37.048
Because of my ecosystem

38:37.048 --> 38:39.951
and what I know
we can bring to the table,

38:39.951 --> 38:42.187
